OL,3,CEnd 'ridiculous' royal tax breaks,
OL,4,CGreens urge in election pledge
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens have said they
OL,7,Fwould end royal tax breaks in Scotland
OL,8,Fas part of their election pledges to
OL,9,F"make the super-rich pay their fair
OL,10,Fshare".
OL,12,FThe party said it was unfair that the
OL,13,F"scandal-ridden" monarchy was given
OL,14,F"perks" while costs were soaring for
OL,15,Fregular people.
OL,17,FCo-leader Ross Greer said it was
OL,18,F"ridiculous" that the King was legally
OL,19,Fexempt from paying a range of taxes.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@FO]uD@AOUuD@PO]vD@AOUvD@GO]zD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@LO]
