CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775001769
OL,3,CEnd 'ridiculous' royal tax breaks,
OL,4,CGreens urge in election pledge
OL,6,FMurdo Fraser, Tory candidate for
OL,7,FPerthshire North, described the calls
OL,8,Fas a "student politics stunt".
OL,10,FHe added: "Ross Greer and his
OL,11,FRepublican pals should grow up instead
OL,12,Fof chucking out unserious policies
OL,13,Fjust to play to the gallery."
OL,15,FThe royal communications office
OL,16,Fadvised that all income received by
OL,17,Fthe King from the Duchy of Lancaster
OL,18,Fis included in his annual tax return.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@]O]rD@KOUuD@]O]
