OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775001769
OL,3,CEnd 'ridiculous' royal tax breaks,
OL,4,CGreens urge in election pledge
OL,6,FThe office also said the sovereign
OL,7,Fpays income tax on a voluntary basis
OL,8,Fat HMRC's additional rate, as well as
OL,9,Fcapital gains tax on all private
OL,10,Fincome, and that the King is subject
OL,11,Fto VAT, also paying local rates on a
OL,12,Fvoluntary basis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
